f Abarim and camped in the plains of Moab by the Jordan at Jericho; </span><span class=\"v4_33_49\"><sup id=\"Num.33.49\" class=\"v4_33_49\">49</sup>they camped by the Jordan from Beth-jeshimoth as far as Abel-shittim in the plains of Moab.</span></p>\n<h3 class=\"s1\">Drive Out the Inhabitants</h3>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"v4_33_50\"><sup id=\"Num.33.50\" class=\"v4_33_50\">50</sup>And the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span> spoke to Moses in the plains of Moab by the Jordan at Jericho, saying, </span><span class=\"v4_33_51\"><sup id=\"Num.33.51\" class=\"v4_33_51\">51</sup>\u201cSpeak to the people of Israel and say to them, When you pass over the Jordan into the land of Canaan, </span><span class=\"v4_33_52\"><sup id=\"Num.33.52\" class=\"v4_33_52\">52</sup>then you shall drive out all the inhabitants of the land from before you and destroy all their figured stones and destroy all their metal images and demolish all their high places. </span><span class=\"v4_33_53\"><sup id=\"Num.33.53\" class=\"v4_33_53\">53</sup>And you shall take possession of the land and settle in it, for I have given the land to you to possess it. </span><span class=\"v4_33_54\"><sup id=\"Num.33.54\" class=\"v4_33_54\">54</sup>You shall inherit the land by lot according to your clans. To a large tribe you shall give a large inheritance, and to a small tribe you shall give a small inheritance. Wherever the lot falls for anyone, that shall be his. According to the tribes of your fathers you shall inherit. </span><span class=\"v4_33_55\"><sup id=\"Num.33.55\" class=\"v4_33_55\">55</sup>But if you do not drive out the inhabitants of the land from before you, then those of them whom you let remain shall be as barbs in your eyes and thorns in your sides, and they shall trouble you in the land where you dwell. </span><span class=\"v4_33_56\"><sup id=\"Num.33.56\" class=\"v4_33_56\">56</sup>And I will do to you as I thought to do to them.\u201d</span></p>\n</div>\n", 
